This plugin is an independent, clean-room reimplementation of the operational
("ops") workflow concepts popularised by c8volt (https://github.com/grafvonb/c8volt),
which is licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later. No c8volt source code was copied; this
is an original TypeScript implementation for the c8ctl plugin system. The command
surface and behaviour are functional descriptions and are not covered by c8volt's
source copyright.
